title.en: Are ga Shitai, Kore ga Hoshii.

description.en: My boss Kuji-san is smart and cool, and everyone admires him...but in fact he loves sex and will sleep with anyone! It was because my dick is bigger than average that Kuji noticed me. Every day, in the toilet, in the meeting room, his face is buried in my crotch. "I want it in me soon ?," my boss invites me. Can my dick keep up!?
